@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<style>

    /* About Us Section */
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    header h1 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
        color: #333;
    }

    section {
        margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

        section h2 {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        section p {
            color: #777;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

            section ul li {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

                section ul li a {
                    color: #555;
                    text-decoration: none;
                }

                    section ul li a:hover {
                        text-decoration: underline;
                    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>About Khumlo Craft</h1>
        </header>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Khumlo Craft, your destination for unique and handcrafted products!</p>
            <p>At Khumlo Craft, we believe in the beauty of craftsmanship and the stories behind each piece. Our journey began with a passion for preserving traditional crafts and providing a platform for artisans to showcase their talents to the world.</p>
            <p>Driven by a commitment to quality and authenticity, we carefully curate our collection to offer you a diverse range of handmade items, from intricately woven textiles to finely carved woodwork.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission at Khumlo Craft is to celebrate craftsmanship while promoting sustainability and supporting local artisans. We strive to bridge the gap between traditional techniques and contemporary designs, ensuring that each purchase you make not only brings joy to your life but also contributes to the livelihood of skilled craftsmen.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
            <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a question about our products, want to collaborate, or simply want to say hello, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
            <p>You can contact us via email at <a href="mailto:info@khumlocraft.com">info@khumlocraft.com</a> or connect with us on social media:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/khumlocraft">Facebook</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://twitter.com/khumlocraft">Twitter</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/khumlocraft">Instagram</a></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
